I hear someone calling me, so Danchou is going to go over there.

360
00:26:21,581 --> 00:26:27,581
まだまだね、ライブは続きますから、ぜひぜひハッシュタグいっぱい呟いて、スクショも撮ってくれると嬉しいです！
The live is still continuing, so please tweet a lot with the hashtag and take screenshots too!

361
00:26:28,081 --> 00:26:33,081
では、行ってきます！ダダダダダダダダ！
Well then, here I go! Dadadadadadada!

362
00:26:38,081 --> 00:26:42,081
